{"tid":1871852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑龍江減少14個確診病例","createTime":"2020-02-09T17:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T00:07:45.000Z","uid":30647,"like":292,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6569728e50cee76faadcab387e62c1b3f5f426","tid":1871852,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:25:58.000Z","msg":"驗到陽性都可以唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n黑龍江當局今日舉行記者會時，宣佈當地減少14個確診病例，官員解釋，<span style=\"color: red;\">國家衞健委日前修訂統計標準，沒有病徵的病人，不再計入確診病例，於是之前當地的13名病人，沒有病徵但檢測呈陽性，於是從確診病例中剔除</span>，與此同時，當地綏化市一名診患者，在海南時已出現發燒病徵，於是，當局認為這病例應該計入海南省。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200209/H3RRNYSOPEJVQK24TXVC77MYZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200209%2FH3RRNYSOPEJVQK24TXVC77MYZI%2F&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=bab129e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200209%2FH3RRNYSOPEJVQK24TXVC77MYZI%2F&h=102f0dcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200209/H3RRNYSOPEJVQK24TXVC77MYZI/</a>"},{"pid":"a8f6e9a037ea8b84c0bbcf360ac11a61512e6da7","tid":1871852,"uid":141833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0433f24d01dca3932bf2afd6bb6444483f555f7a","tid":1871852,"uid":9412,"like":151,"dislike":3,"score":148,"quote":{"pid":"bf6569728e50cee76faadcab387e62c1b3f5f426","tid":1871852,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:25:58.000Z","msg":"驗到陽性都可以唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n黑龍江當局今日舉行記者會時，宣佈當地減少14個確診病例，官員解釋，<span style=\"color: red;\">國家衞健委日前修訂統計標準，沒有病徵的病人，不再計入確診病例，於是之前當地的13名病人，沒有病徵但檢測呈陽性，於是從確診病例中剔除</span>，與此同時，當地綏化市一名診患者，在海南時已出現發燒病徵，於是，當局認為這病例應該計入海南省。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200209/H3RRNYSOPEJVQK24TXVC77MYZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200209%2FH3RRNYSOPEJVQK24TXVC77MYZI%2F&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=bab129e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200209%2FH3RRNYSOPEJVQK24TXVC77MYZI%2F&h=102f0dcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200209/H3RRNYSOPEJVQK24TXVC77MYZI/</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:27:45.000Z","msg":"唔夠測劑驗個D唔計 <br />\n冇病徵唔計<br />\n唔係醫院死個D又唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea36ffa730c0d883476fa06ba33263950149502","tid":1871852,"uid":47198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f78f07ddf0fe707f15c74ce106bcb74ea78ff72","tid":1871852,"uid":73340,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"降低確診標準線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b264f422abbac22db967ac3012dc7dce36dbbdd0","tid":1871852,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b263725b27f43945c632a0438ec11d3ee0e669d3","tid":1871852,"uid":265179,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:28:58.000Z","msg"