es/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cbd74ae272a0ed9a10f4ae560fae1cdd6c3266","tid":1871852,"uid":229830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T18:11:18.000Z","msg":"office hour 先計啦不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1607dce38a70d63cc9bfcd1634ec84ccd5c60915","tid":1871852,"uid":307607,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"ab4bf06b2a1608190d8a0add66d43dc6525fa97d","tid":1871852,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"如何才算確診武漢肺炎系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"怎麼才算在中國確診武漢肺炎?<br />\n1.要由中國醫生認證<br />\n2.要在感染者沒有併發症的時候中招<br />\n3.要由飛沫傳播<br />\n4.你不能沒有肚瀉<br />\n5.你不能沒有咳嗽<br />\n6.你不能沒有吃過野味，你要吃過所有品種的蝙蝠<br />\n7.你不能在人煙稀薄的地方中招，要給中國醫生用「在人多地方出現」作為確診理由<br />\n8.你不能曾經在測試中呈陰性反應<br />\n9.在中國，你不能有私家醫生，要由政府確認你確診<br />\n10.你不能沒有發燒<br />\n11.你不能死亡<br />\n12.你確診前要由醫院所有胸肺科醫生確認，最好全省的胸肺科醫生都確認，這樣才是真確診，否則醫生都會認為是普通感冒<br />\n13.你的肺要全白<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心確診了，政府也會說你是其他疾病，說你是發燒，說你腸胃炎。政府總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不是確診。"},{"pid":"cb48b2d8112d69043eba989e3de016c59e243207","tid":1871852,"uid":120772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba6cc46be8c85a2d8505fd56e46b73b9abae4666","tid":1871852,"uid":40010,"like":128,"dislike":1,"score":127,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:30:09.000Z","msg":"不如星期135先計<br />\n246日就唔算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"笑出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a31f313803e7c1ff576da81cfb2b49681dab0c6","tid":1871852,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci